{"tid":2088131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[問路] 由銅鑼灣香港大廈搭咩車去到油麻地獨立大廈","createTime":"2020-07-01T04:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:34:09.000Z","uid":147226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39730a5eaf77b81a0ce1084d4c216531566fee48","tid":2088131,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"儲啲 AEON 積分儲到就快過期要換野<br />\n痴佢個線全香港得幾間 AEON 可以換，平時果啲吉之島話唔換得，要走去銅鑼灣香港大廈分行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有啲野要搞，要去汽車交通運輸業總工會九龍分會 (工聯會野，但無辦法，唔關我事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n(地址: 油麻地彌敦道499-501A號獨立大廈三樓)<br />\n<br />\n跟住要去土瓜灣間招商永隆銀行，間野成個香港無分行咁滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港</strong>大廈 （銅鑼灣） &gt;<br />\n<strong>獨立</strong>大廈 （油麻地）&gt;<br />\n<strong>唯一</strong>大廈 （土瓜灣）<br />\n<br />\n住開新界，驚搭地鐵唔識<strong>出</strong>，蕩失<strong>路</strong>，求巴士<br />\n但首先要出咗銅鑼灣先 (咪點去 AEON 換野)"},{"pid":"2834f224baf6d03e5196b8a6e5501c6c86b12fb3","tid":2088131,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}